Creating superior value with unrivaled wisdom






Our Business
Founded nearly 30 years ago, Peter J. Solomon Company (PJSC) is a leading financial advisory firm on Wall Street with a legacy as one of the
                first independent investment banks. We advise clients on mergers, acquisitions, sales, restructurings, recapitalizations, capital markets solutions and activism defense across
                a range of industries, including retail, media and entertainment, infrastructure and energy.
Our difference is that we offer unmatched industry knowledge in the sectors we cover, going deep into those sectors to provide the most comprehensive
                strategic solutions, tailored to generate long-term shareholder value.
WE ARE THE BEST OF ALL WORLDS.  Today Peter J. Solomon Company is an independently-run affiliate of Natixis, part of Groupe BPCE, a top ten
                European and top 20 global bank. As such, our clients enjoy proprietary access to an international advisory and financing platform with
                coverage throughout North and South America, EMEA and Asia.



Practice Areas:

Mergers & AcquisitionsM&A is at the core of PJSC’s advisory services. We partner with clients to stimulate creative strategic solutions. 
Restructuring & RecapitalizationWe have led some of the largest and most complex restructuring transactions over the past 20 years. 
Special Committee & Fairness Opinion PracticeWe bring an independent voice to Special Committees and Board of Directors on a wide range of transactions. 
Financing AdvisoryFree from conflicts, we advise clients in accessing the public capital markets as well as highly tailored, bespoke capital from                             specialty lenders, hedge funds and other institutional investors. 
Activist DefenseWe advise management teams and Boards of Directors on their vulnerability to, and defense from, shareholder activism and unsolicited                             or hostile takeover bids.  







Industry Expertise:

Global RetailWith a deep heritage in the retailing industry, our unique cross-sector approach and creative strategies help to generate long-term                             shareholder value. 
Food Retail & RestaurantsOur team provides investment banking advisory services to clients across various food retail and restaurant subsectors. 
E-commerce & Retail TechnologyPJSC has one of the largest senior banking teams dedicated to advising clients on how they engage with and distribute products                             to consumers. 
Technology, Media & TelecommunicationsAs disruption becomes the new normal, we are in the forefront of the fast-changing media, technology and communications landscapes. 
EnergyThe PJSC Energy Advisory Group provides strategic investment banking advisory services to public and private clients across the                             energy chain. 
InfrastructureProviding private equity, pension and infrastructure funds, corporate and municipal clients with a full suite of strategic and financial advisory services. 
Real EstateWe provide real estate financing, sales and valuation services for private and public companies. 








 

Our People See Now
Our personal, responsive approach emphasizes relationships, not transactions, and is at the heart of our concept of investment banking.





Recruiting See Now
PJSC’s recruiting philosophy is to pursue individuals with diverse backgrounds who are creative, highly motivated and possess strong
                        analytical and quantitative skills.
 
Peter J. Solomon Company is ranked #13 in the Vault Guide to the Top 50 Banking Employers.



