 Our Business


Our Business






Uncompromised advice and innovative solutions 
A successful investment banking relationship requires that the investment banker understand the values and aspirations of the client. These values and
    goals are usually not apparent immediately, nor is the client always certain at the outset of a project how to weigh and value the components of a
    successful outcome.
Peter J. Solomon Company listens carefully to clients and works with them to articulate their key objectives. Once we understand their goals, we use quantitative
    analysis and informed experience to determine the course of action most likely to attain their goals.


Practice Areas:
 Mergers & Acquisitions
M&A is at the core of PJSC’s advisory services. We partner with clients to stimulate creative strategic solutions.
