 Careers at Peter J Solomon


Careers






A Place to Grow
Because of our entrepreneurial nature, PJSC encourages our employees to assume increasing levels of responsibility commensurate with their
                    progress. As a result, PJSC believes our professionals develop important client and deal experience earlier than their peers at larger,
                    more structured investment banking firms. If you are resourceful, energetic and demonstrate initiative, you can build a career at PJSC.
                    We regularly promote our junior bankers up through the ranks. 
People who have demonstrated leadership skills, who can flourish in a team environment and who are flexible by nature and creative in their
                    thinking will thrive at our firm.
We recruit the best and brightest. This is what we look for in candidates: 
 


 » Leadership Skills » Highly Motivated » Team Players 



 » Strong Analytical & Quantitative Skills » Strong Communication Skills » Creative Thinking 







 
Peter J. Solomon Company is ranked #13 in the Vault Guide to the Top 50 Banking Employers. Read the Vault review 







PJSC Culture
PJSC’s culture is built on honesty, integrity and a collective commitment to providing clients with sound, unbiased advice. We are guided
                    on a daily basis by these values and pursue them in a collaborative environment that promotes excellence and creativity.
                     
 Intellectual Integrity
Clients retain PJSC to render objective conclusions about strategic decisions which affect their capitalizations. Our advice is free
                        from conflicts of interest. The partnership does not invest for its own account, trade securities, provide research or manage client
                        assets. Relationship Focused
Our personal, responsive approach emphasizes relationships, not transactions, and is at the heart of our concept of investment banking.
                        A dedicated team remains with the client throughout every project. We Give Back
We encourage and support our people to engage in the non-profit world whether through volunteer projects, participation in charitable
                        events or donating their time in non-profit board positions.



















