peter j solomon co lp
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Institutional Financial Svcs
Sub-Industry: Institutional Brokerage
Peter J. Solomon Company is an investment banking firm. The firm specializes in mergers and acquisitions, as well as provides counsel to corporate boards and renders fairness opinions. Peter J. Solomon Company also offers advisory services and assists companies on financial restructurings.




